{"tid":1747792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「黎明行動」聽日選舉行動方案！","createTime":"2019-11-23T11:20:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T15:17:43.000Z","uid":107998,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a5812c8293c655058c204cca5c24d9aec06c129b","tid":1747792,"uid":107998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:20:39.000Z","msg":"根據2016年選民數字，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>61歲嘅選民</strong></span>係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">18到40歲嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">總和</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n所以<span style=\"font-size: large;\">千祈唔好以為自己投完票就完成任務</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">記得關心自己嘅屋企人。</span></strong></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n樓主為大家提供以下方案：<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">方案<span style=\"color: teal;\">一</span></span></strong>：<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屋企人係<span style=\"color: teal;\">藍絲</span></span></strong>，請你朝早靜雞雞去投票，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">話佢聽投票站啲popo，會傳播二噁英架。</span></span>然後同全家人享天倫之樂。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">Tips：</span></strong></span>有幾遠去幾遠，有幾夜玩幾夜。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">方案<span style=\"color: green;\">二</span>：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屋企人係<span style=\"color: green;\">中立</span></span></strong>，請你務必<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">比往日更加孝順，更加關心老一輩。</span></span>朝早同全家人飲茶，然後一齊去投票。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">Tips：</span></span></strong>話俾佢知投幾多號、男定女、外觀特徵。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">方案<span style=\"color: gold;\">三</span>：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">屋企人係<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃絲</span></span></strong>，恭喜你，確保屋企人有投票就得啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F28dT2a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF28dT2a.png&h=a82c93e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">乖孫一言，建制難追</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"745a9676e6152fe34be554d5b7a56cd82d03d1ff","tid":1747792,"uid":107998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:23:44.000Z","msg":"推 1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ed892e91ccd504b24ac758c6f30a6975f55e476","tid":1747792,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:25:48.000Z","msg":"[深度數據分析] 你知道嗎？多你一票好多<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ezEbiS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ezEbiS</a>"},{"pid":"58dc9a1459cc5a1664a579ffb2e58fc14e4d8bec","tid":1747792,"uid":107998,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:29:37.000Z","msg":"推 2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd2ff1e135d49b3da9d9cbfb5f98b86d05c5f53","tid":1747792,"uid":319818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:34:20.000Z","msg":"e個要大力推"},{"pid":"7876ddaf702520ddfed75d61cc513bd31c04a6e4","tid":1747792,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T11:34:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">push<br />\n多你一個做野好多</span>"},{"pid":"024a82522c7a54f4d39cec465b20254a7ecaa833","tid":1747792,"uid":238374,"li